        <item>
            <title>日本名古屋铁道试行「空手观光」   去机场前托运行李 + GPS 标签可追踪</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/16/japan-travel-luggage/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=japan-travel-luggage</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/16/japan-travel-luggage/life-tech/travel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 08:00:39 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅游]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1220210</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[
<p class="-ml-3 md:ml-0"><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">据日媒报道，</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">日本名古屋铁道公司、名古屋车站及中部国际机场将在</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">中部国际机场和北海道新千岁机场的部分航班测试</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">「空手观光」，让游客可在去机场前预先报到后托运行李。<br /></span></p><p class="-ml-3 md:ml-0"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1220318" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/047screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/047screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/047screenshot.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p class="-ml-3 md:ml-0"><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">据富士新闻网报道，现时旅客</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">去机场前可以在名古屋车站寄存行李，</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">预先报到后</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">登记托运行李</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">就能直接将行李</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">送上预定航班。这项措施能够节省旅客</span><span class="border-primary mb-6 block border-l-4 pl-3 md:mb-8">在机场排队报到的时间。</span>旅客于名古屋车站寄存行李后，工作人员会将托运行李送上专车，寄送往日本中部国际机场。工作人员会在行李上贴 GPS 标签，让旅客追踪行李位置。</p><p>日本希望「空手观光」计划可缩短旅客于机场等待的时间，从而减低航空公司压力，以及纾缓排队人潮。据悉日本目标是在 2025 年大阪关西世博前正式落实上述措施。</p><p><div class="video-container"><iframe title="回送列车で运び搭乗机まで…『手ぶら旅行』の実证実験，駅で荷物预けて手ぶらで空港へ 名鉄等が実用化目指す" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/IpNl-DB2_Z4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.fnn.jp/articles/-/657472">FNN</a>、<a href="https://udn.com/news/story/6812/7754547">联合新闻网</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/16/japan-travel-luggage/life-tech/travel/">日本名古屋铁道试行「空手观光」   去机场前托运行李 + GPS 标签可追踪</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
